summary: Just a rename for Uthgerd the Unbroken. The main content of the file is not my own but Bethesda's. I only have just renamed the character.
descriptionHtml:
Maud's favorite weapon of choice is her rod of sparks. She sometimes continues to shock her foes even after they have fallen to her mighty blade.
<br />This mod is for a small youtuber that I watch regularly. Her channel is www.youtube.com/user/khaligames. If anyone sees this go check her out.Â
